pro_course_detail.description:
This course is for you if: 
*you need to prepare for TORFL or another exam; 
*you study in Russia and need help with your studying (for example with your written assignments); 
*you are going to visit Russian-speaking countries and need to prepare for this trip;
*you need to translate or correct something; 
*you want to improve your pronunciation, etc.
Text me in advance in order to explain your request.

teacher_info.teaching_style:
▶My regular lesson lasts 60 minutes. I prefer to start my lessons with warm-up exercises. 
Then we proceed to the main part of the lesson, the plan depends on a particular student. 

▶What we usually do:
- read and discuss texts/stories;
- watching and discussing videos;
- learn grammar and practice it in oral and written form;
- listen to stories/dialogues.

▶I use interactive tasks, games, quizzes, flashcards. They engage both visual and aural memory.
At the end of the class, I provide a student with the homework. Systematic homework preparation is a crucial element in achieving a good result. I insist on doing homework and always give attention to its fulfillment.

pro_course_detail.description:
This course is designed for foreign students who want to learn the Verbs of Motion from scratch or to develop their skills and understanding of the Verbs of Motion.

It is suitable for students with basic knowledge of Russian. The explanation is given in English and provided in a condensed and understandable way.

This course gives a proper explanation of the idea of unidirectional and multidirectional verbs. Students will learn the most common ways of using the verbs in the Past, Present, and Future tenses. They will learn how to distinguish the unidirectional and multidirectional verbs and choose the one they need. 

The course contains an interactive workbook that students fill in when watching the lectures. The workbook has theoretical material, exercises that check students’ understanding of the lecture, and space to take notes. Moreover, after each exercise, the student gets not just the key answer but also a detailed explanation of each correct answer.

* Course duration is 2 hours;
* 30 pages PDF Workbook; 
* After booking the course, you will get a link to download the course and the Workbook;


* Check the extract from the course: https://youtu.be/L72EJUSEFew

*If you have any questions, please text me in PM.
